Q1. UI Design Challenge (AI-Assisted )

Design a homepage for a college web app using a computer with the help of AI tools (such as ChatGPT, Copilot, etc.).

Requirements:
Your webpage should include:

College name and logo (text/logo image)
Navigation menu (Home, Courses, Events, Contact)
Student details section (Name, ID, Department)
Announcements / Notice board
At least 2 interactive elements (buttons, links, etc.)

Instructions:

You are allowed to use AI tools to generate HTML/CSS/JS code
You must understand and modify the code generated by AI
Only HTML, CSS (and basic JavaScript if needed) should be used
No ready-made templates or design software allowed

Judging Criteria:

Creativity (Unique layout and design)
Usability (Easy to navigate)
Code Quality (Clean and understandable code)
Smart Use of AI (How well AI tools are used and improved)

Expected Output:

A working HTML file opened in browser

Example Idea:
A simple webpage with:

Header showing college name
Menu bar with links
Student info card
Notice board section
Buttons like “Login” or “View Results”
